&lt;br&gt; 
&lt;ul&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#why-generative-engine-optimizations-roi-is-higher-than-ever"&gt;Why generative engine optimization’s ROI is higher than ever&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
