&lt;ul&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#what-is-digital-marketing-optimization"&gt;What is digital marketing optimization?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#how-digital-marketing-optimization-works-across-the-lifecycle"&gt;How digital marketing optimization works across the lifecycle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#digital-marketing-optimization-strategies-you-can-use-now"&gt;Digital marketing optimization strategies you can use now&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
